## Important Notes on Medical Use

This software is provided for **research and educational purposes only**. 

**Disclaimer:**
- NOT intended for clinical diagnosis or medical decision-making
- NOT FDA-approved or validated for clinical use
- Should only be used by qualified medical professionals in research contexts
- Predictions should ALWAYS be verified by qualified clinicians
- Do not rely solely on this system for any medical decisions

**Data Privacy:**
- When using this software with patient data:
  - Ensure HIPAA/GDPR compliance
  - Obtain proper informed consent
  - De-identify all personally identifiable information
  - Implement appropriate access controls and encryption
  - Maintain audit trails for data access

**Liability:**
The authors assume NO liability for:
- Misuse of the software
- Clinical errors resulting from misinterpretation
- Data breaches or privacy violations
- Performance in settings different from training data

